com.tallygo.tallygoandroid.sdk.route

Class TGRoute

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tallygo.tallygoandroid.sdk.TGBaseObject
      • com.tallygo.tallygoandroid.sdk.route.TGRoute

  • public class TGRoute
extends TGBaseObject
    A class to represent a TallyGo route. Because this object may be large for extremely long routes use TGRouteRepository to move routes between contexts.
